def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('a', 'aA')

print(insert_after_character('banana'))  # banaAna
print(insert_after_character('apple'))  # apple
print(insert_after_character('cat'))  # cAt
print(insert_after_character('dog'))  # dog
print(insert_after_character('aardvark'))  # aAardvArk
